<br>
Every item that the guild replaces on a toon goes back to the guild.. for example-- you have a black enameled breast plate currently on your cleric, on a hate raid you are awarded an em bp. The enameled breastplate goes back to the guild, the guild then sells it for guild funds. Also any extra items that no one can use goes to the guild bank for selling at a later time.<br>
<br>
This way on any raid, be it PoA, PoH, HoT.. all raid items are paid for via guild. <p></a><br>
